        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "DEBATE - The House proceeded with one hour of debate on H.R. 2270.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H8D000",
        "actionDate": "2026-01-13",
        "actionTime": "14:32:57",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "Rule provides for consideration of H.R. 2988, H.R. 2262, H.R. 2270, H.R. 2312 and H.R. 4366. The resolution provides for consideration of H.R. 2988 under a structured rule, and H.R. 2262, H.R. 2270, H.R. 2312, and H.R. 4366 under a closed rule. The rule provides for one hour of general debate and one motion to recommit on each bill.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H30000",
        "actionDate": "2026-01-13",
        "actionTime": "14:32:52",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "Considered under the provisions of rule H. Res. 988. (consideration: CR H681-685; text of amendment in the nature of a substitute: CR H681)",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
